imp.core.commands.data

Class DataYSlideCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • imp.core.commands.data.DataPrismCommand
      • imp.core.commands.data.DataYSlideCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Command

    public class DataYSlideCommand
extends DataPrismCommand
    Class for instantiating the data in an YSlide joint to be something other than the default values. The execute method to be used is identical to the one in the Data Prism Command since the only difference is a question of axis, and that is handled by the constructor.
    Version:
    1.01
    Author:
    dykstran
